In [6]:
# Create a TSNE instance: model
model = TSNE(learning_rate=50,perplexity=30)

# Apply fit_transform to normalized_movements: tsne_features
tsne_features = model.fit_transform(traffic_accidents_numeric)
In [7]:
traffic_accidents_tsne_features = pd.DataFrame(tsne_features,columns=['Xs','Ys'])
